Steps to install SASS:

1. Installed Node Version Manager (NVM) by running:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed and reopened the terminal to load NVM.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0 using:
   nvm install 20.16.0

4. Installed SASS globally with npm:
   npm install -g sass

5. Verified the installation by running:
   sass --version
